Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候已久的時刻到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了證明許多英靈並非平白喪生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2號機？在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米島的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為再次高揭ZION的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦為成就「星塵」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門啊！我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}激突戰域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這、這就是「星塵」嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的，不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多還真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪大人，時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今就動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉向右5度，第2戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是凱風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防艇還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ES-11請求增援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5號閘門不能使用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內還有船員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS不能出動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害區域42%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的MS竟做出這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還事情沒了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將本艦轉向金米島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒了斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動啊，左腕不能動了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐，太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出預期的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我們這三年也有回報了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那些游手好閒的傢伙們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是所謂的惡夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，待會見，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在預訂地點恭候您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的不堪一擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正下方？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多，聽到嗎？回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能聽到的吧，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你忘了，我也絕不會忘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次那個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒了斷前我不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這只是為我的勝仗錦上添花而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過對你沒什麼可多費唇舌的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對，卡多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多，聽不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各艦前往第10區
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12號閘門在封鎖中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SL的殘存部隊集結到L23
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7區域損害率87%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各艦隊都受到很大的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約有2/3無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就算只剩1/3的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍遠佔優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而相反的他們已用掉了底牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將旗艦轉為「茲隆」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後進行周圍巡哨及艦隊的重新編製
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂來電「前來救援」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還來幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說港區很混亂反而會添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取獨立的索敵攻擊部隊所應有的自由行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足了吧，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那對2號機被奪走的我們而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恥辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來把他惹火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,582
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就聽聽看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨是戰鬥起源的本因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但憑怨恨支持戰鬥的人打不倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我站在「義」字之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做為齒輪而戰的人不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左腕不能動？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手長進了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這兩人非得戰鬥不可呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，主攝像機…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我和你的價值觀終究是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，脫離吧，快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 Core Fighter不能用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你叫浦木吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不會忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信已中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉也平安脫離了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是草莓9號，草莓9號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在125地點巡哨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉眼確認了移動中的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓9號請繼續巡哨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米島的事就像假的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那像是鯨魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯨魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎麼啦，摩拉，沒頭沒腦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像平時的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂頭喪氣地躲在房裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我失去了1號機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對妮娜而言是因為同時失去了1號和2號機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅如此嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，只有你能鼓勵她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是高茲，聽到請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人應答嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是高茲，聽到請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，被干擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座殖民地由我們殖民地公社管理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是宇宙住民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地可說是我們生活的基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM所引發的事全都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩架GUNDAM都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興你能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，今後該怎麼辦？妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地球也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宏一起的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不認為一切都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多的…他的態度…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「星塵」仍然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再提那個人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今後戰鬥仍將持續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過投入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至滲透到身體之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想忘掉這一切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是萊因巴克1號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達與巡哨機失去聯絡的地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都平安無事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被聯邦查覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派出狼群
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎太遲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS全機退避完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦主炮一起射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持殖民地？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時爆破了兩座殖民地的鏡面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持無人的殖民地想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找兩位來不為別的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想你們聽聽我今後的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上我認為「星塵」的本質目前尚未顯露出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說金米島襲擊可能是某種前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則迪拉茲為什麼發表那樣的演說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是恐嚇…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遵從賈布羅的高雲將軍的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定續行對迪拉茲艦隊的戰鬥行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將GUNDAM的1號機和2號機運到了澳大利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為需要做重力狀態下地面測試的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那兩架吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不在我管轄之內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在…3號機…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若以中尉的資歷加上妮娜小姐技術的支持…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，請務必讓我擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，那完全是另一種機型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦已變更了航向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往正於3-5-B地點為測試而航行的「玫瑰人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緊急情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持殖民地？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這鏡面爆破是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩1分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我想像得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自失去一片鏡面的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重心就會偏移，會產生回轉傾斜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久它們就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會相撞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然，相撞的殖民地會彼此彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個會被月球重力所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對月球的殖民地墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將此事報告金米島
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，讓本艦也轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個位置趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒殖民地相撞時的放電
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳來殖民地相撞的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一座殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定會向月球的拉格朗治點墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道情況會如何變化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在先去把GUNDAM…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.63,0:25:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預    告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.27,0:25:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「星塵」在等離子空間覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.30,0:25:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球牽引著孤獨的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.70,0:25:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在需要的是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.78,0:25:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂為取得GUNDAM3號機造訪了「玫瑰人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.49,0:25:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時鐘永無停止的指針
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.35,0:25:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木焦躁的心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.42,0:25:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聳立的GUNDAM3號機眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.20,0:25:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間在迫使妮娜下決定
